{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 73,
  "title": "第七十三章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "勇於敢則殺，"
    },
    {
      "text": "勇於不敢則活。"
    },
    {
      "text": "此兩者，或利或害。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天之所惡，孰知其故？是以聖人猶難之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天之道，不爭而善勝，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不言而善應，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不召而自來，"
    },
    {
      "text": "繟然而善謀。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天網恢恢，疏而不失。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "必不得其死也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "必齊命也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "俱勇而所施者異，利害不同，故曰，或利或害也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孰，誰也。言誰能知天下之所惡意故邪？其唯聖人。夫聖人之明，猶難於勇敢，況無聖人之明而欲行之也。故曰，猶難之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天唯不爭，故天下莫能與之爭。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "順則吉，逆則凶，不言而善應也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "處下則物自歸。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "垂象而見吉凶，先事而設誠，安而不忘危，未召而謀之，故曰，繟然而善謀也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
